===Noun Phrase===
'''bubonic plague'''

# {{pathology}} A contagious, often fatal, epidemic disease caused by the [[bacterium]] ''Yersinia pestis'', transmitted by the bite of [[flea]]s from an infected person or [[rodent]], especially a [[rat]], and characterized by [[delirium]], chills, fever, vomiting, [[diarrhea]], and the formation of [[bubo]]es.

